<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><author>mạhr fạyz, mạhr fạyz</author>
<hymn_number>1576</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr- kl ạlmạḍy bysẖhd .. lyk wlḥbk wrʿạytk lynạ
 wạlḥạḍr wạljạy fy ạ̹ydyk .. bạlḥmd hạysẖhd lk fynạ
 1- mạbnnsạsẖ mạbnnsạsẖ ạlạ̹yd ạlḥlwẗ
 ạlly ạtmtdt wqt ạlạ̉zmạt
 wlạ nnsạsẖ wlạ ymkn ạ̉bdaⁿạ rạḥ nnsy̱
 tʿzyạtk fy ạlậlạmạt
 2- mạbnnsạsẖ mạbnnsạsẖ ạlnʿmẗ
 ạlly btrfʿ wtṣwn wqt ạlḍʿfạt
 qwẗ dmk qwẗ dmk wsẖfạʿtk
 wạlrwḥ ysẖfʿ fynạ bạ̉nạt
 3- mạbnnsạsẖ ạ̹n fy ạ̉mrạḍnạ blmsẗ btsẖfy
 wṣwtk ydy ạlqlb ḥyạẗ
 nbḍ ʿrwqnạ nbḍ ʿrwqnạ ạlly fy ạ̉jsạdnạ
 bysẖhd ʿn ạ̹ḥsạn ạllh
 4- yạmạ nsynạ yạmạ nsynạ ạ̉mạntk lynạ
 wkẖwnạ ạlqlb ạlly mạsbnạsẖ
 wạ̉mạ rjʿnạ ạ̉mạ rjʿnạ fy lḥẓẗ lqynạ
 ḥbk ṣạdq mạbtnsạsẖ</lyrics>
<title>kl ạlmạḍy bysẖhd lyk</title>
</song>